text: Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife, also Province of Santa Cruz (), is a province of Spain, made up of the western part of the autonomous community of the Canary Islands. It has the islands of Tenerife, La Gomera, El Hierro, and La Palma. It occupies an area of .Auditorio de Tenerife (in Spanish) ==References==
